  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 0504cc30fbfddc244a5ee9fef0d9a9d1, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ProjectNotes
  notes: 'Run 01:

    Kill reward +1

    Hit reward +0.5

    Sight reward +0.001

    Step
    penalty -0.001

    Death penalty -1

    ---

    Tanks didn''t learn very well.
    Tanks may have been reward hacking the sight reward, and they spam fired the
    whole time.

    ---

    Run 02:

    Kill reward +2.5

    Hit reward +1

    Step
    penalty -0.001

    Hitting nothing penalty -0.01

    Getting hit penalty -0.25

    Death
    penalty -1

    ---

    Tanks still didn''t learn. They followed the same trajectory
    as before.

    ---

    Run 03:

    Same rewards as Run 02, but YAML reconfigured:

    Buffer
    Size: 20,000 --> 50,000

    Batch Size: 512 --> 1024

    Time Horizon: 128
    --> 256'
